Title: Kyss FM 102.5 FM Sandy Point Town, Saint Kitts-Nevis
Description: KYSS FM is a privately owned FM radio station. Our broadcast studio is located in the istoric town of Sandy Point, on the beautiful 68sq mile island of St. Kitts in the West Indies.We operate 24hrs per day seven days a week on the assigned frequency of 102.5Mkz on the FM band.You can listen to the widest variety of music genres, R&B, Hip Hop, Rap, Country, Reggae, Dancehall, Soca, Calypso, Gospel and Our local riddims.
